    <title>xf86-input-synaptics-&xf86-input-synaptics-version;</title>

    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introduction</title>

      <para>
        The xf86-input-synaptics package contains the X.Org Input Driver,
        support programs and SDK for Synaptics touchpads.
      </para>

